    <element name="Eyes of the Watcher" type="Magic Item" source="Raventhemylo" id="ID_RTM_MAGIC_ITEM_EYES_OF_THE_WATCHER">
        <description>
            <p>These bloodred eyes allow their user to learn certain information about a creature's capabilities compared to their own.</p>
            <p>The DM tells you if the creature is your equal, superior, or inferior in regard to two of the following characteristics of your choice:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Strength Score</li>
                <li>Dexterity Score</li>
                <li>Constitution Score</li>
                <li>Armor Class</li>
                <li>Current Hit Points</li>
                <li>Total Class Levels</li>
            </ul>
        </description>

        <setters>
            <set name="category">Wondrous Items</set>
